---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="服務項目 | ITUNG NAILS 伊特美甲" description="ITUNG NAILS 伊特美甲提供凝膠美甲、手足深層保養、占星開運美甲、指甲彩繪、光療延甲與美甲教學。日本材料、平價高CP值。">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-8 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <nav class="text-sm text-it-text mb-4">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-it-cta">首頁</a> <span class="mx-2">/</span> <span>服務項目</span>
      </nav>
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4">伊特美甲服務項目</h1>
        <p class="text-it-text max-w-2xl mx-auto">日本材料、專業技術，從日常美甲到藝術彩繪、占星開運，滿足各種需求。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-6 h-6 text-it-cta flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01"/></svg>凝膠美甲</h2>
          <p class="text-it-text mb-4">使用日本材料，專業凝膠上色，色彩飽和持久。從單色、貓眼、法式、漸層到暈染皆可執行。</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-it-text space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>單色凝膠</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$699 起</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>貓眼 / 漸層 / 法式</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$899 起</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>造型加購（暈染等）</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">依設計報價</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-6 h-6 text-it-cta flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01"/></svg>指甲彩繪</h2>
          <p class="text-it-text mb-4">手繪技術純熟，可自帶圖參考。從簡約線條到世界名畫、動漫角色、油畫玫瑰、花磚、復古窗花等精緻設計。</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-it-text space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>簡單手繪款</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$1,200 起</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>複雜彩繪/客製化</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$1,800 起</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>每月主題特價款</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">請關注 IG</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div id="care" class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-6 h-6 text-it-cta flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"/></svg>手足深層保養</h2>
          <p class="text-it-text mb-4">不只是指尖，保養範圍延伸到整支手臂與小腿。搭配蜂蠟磨砂去角質與淨白凍膜，讓肌膚回到細緻柔嫩。</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-it-text space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>手部深層保養（到肩膀）</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$900 起</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>足部深層保養（到膝蓋）</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$1,000 起</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>包含：卸甲、修型、去角質、凍膜、指緣護理</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta"></span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div id="extension" class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-6 h-6 text-it-cta flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z"/></svg>占星開運美甲</h2>
          <p class="text-it-text mb-4">獨家特色服務！結合星盤分析與星座幸運色，打造專屬於你的開運能量美甲。與豐傑生醫合作，提供星座幸運石造型設計。</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-it-text space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>占星美甲（含星盤）</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$5,200</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>流年攻略占星諮詢</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$5,200</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>單一事項占星諮詢</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$3,600</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>感情合盤</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$7,200</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-6 h-6 text-it-cta flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/></svg>光療延甲</h2>
          <p class="text-it-text mb-4">改善甲型問題，打造完美長度與弧度。適合指甲較短或甲型不整者。深層保養流程已包含指甲建構加固。</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-it-text space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>單指延甲</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$130-150</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>全手延甲</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$1,000 起</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-6 h-6 text-it-cta flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/></svg>美甲教學</h2>
          <p class="text-it-text mb-4">由經驗豐富的美甲師帶領，從基礎到進階，適合想學習美甲技術或轉職的朋友。</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-it-text space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>美甲全科班</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">請洽詢</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>彩繪教學課程</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">請洽詢</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>穿戴甲教學</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">請洽詢</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/courses" class="text-it-cta font-medium hover:text-it-dark transition-colors">了解課程內容 →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 bg-it-light rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-it-dark mb-4">兩間分店預約方式</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-it-dark mb-2">景美店</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-it-text">台北市文山區景興路，近景美捷運站</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-it-text mt-1 flex items-center gap-1"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-it-cta" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>02-2934-9297</p>
            <a href="https://lin.ee/OCPxzKS" target="_blank" class="inline-block mt-2 px-4 py-2 bg-it-cta text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-it-cta/90 transition-colors">LINE 預約景美店</a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-it-dark mb-2">新店店</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-it-text">新店眷村巷弄內，近新店區公所捷運站1號出口</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-it-text mt-1 flex items-center gap-1"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-it-cta" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>02-8665-6288</p>
            <a href="https://lin.ee/KFIGAfw" target="_blank" class="inline-block mt-2 px-4 py-2 bg-it-cta text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-it-cta/90 transition-colors">LINE 預約新店店</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-8 text-center text-sm text-it-text">* 以上價格僅供參考，實際價格依現場報價為準。</p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
